    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>Have you any small change, sir?</text>
      <textCn>先生，您有零钱吗？</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>I'm sorry.</text>
      <textCn>对不起。</textCn>
    </sentence>
